org.netbeans.api.java.source.support

Interface ProfileSupport.ViolationCollector

  • Enclosing class:
    ProfileSupport

    public static interface ProfileSupport.ViolationCollector
    Asynchronous callback for collecting the profile ProfileSupport.Violations. For each classpath or source root a new ProfileSupport.ViolationCollector is created by the ProfileSupport.ViolationCollectorFactory.create(java.net.URL). When the validation of the root is done the finished() is called. Threading: Validations of individual roots may run in parallel depending on the Executor throughput.
